abstract: >-
  A modern, lightweight and composable entity resolution library for Python:
  one swappable matching "brain" (a judge) behind one seam — string
  similarity, embeddings, or an LLM judge — tunable with zero labeled data.
keywords:
  - entity-resolution
  - record-linkage
  - deduplication
  - data-matching
  - llm
